snippet.title: Filmymoji || Middle Class Madhu || Saradaaga || A Family Picnic || MCM
snippet.description:
Filmymoji || Middle Class Madhu || Saradaaga || A Family Picnic || MCM

In this new saradaga episode of Middle Class Madhu, a funny discussion starts between 1A Master and his wife Bhagyam. The discussion later turns into a serious plan when Bhagyam asks him to plan a picnic with the colony. She motivates 1A Master to be the mastermind behind the picnic plan while they portray the plan being executed by Sarada Subbarao. Finally, after convincing sarada Subba Rao, the picnic plan gets started. In surprise, Budatha invites his girlfriend Geetha to the picnic. Seeing Geetha madhu surprises him and he tries to put a fight between Geetha and Budatha, but his plan turns out to be profitable for Budatha. Everybody enjoys the places in Vizag, and Madhu, with his Naatu Guntala Gang, starts funny plans to make the picnic even more funnier. 1A master who is so excited and looking happy in the picnic was the target for Madhu and His Gang. Watch out for this fun-filled episode, Saradaga! And we promise you a 30-minute fun ride.

snippet.description:
England created history on day 1 of the first Test match by scoring the most runs on an opening day. England batters were simply brilliant as they came with the right intent against Pakistan and smashed the bowlers all over the park. England ended Day 1 on high as Zak Crawley, Ben Duckett, Ollie Pope and Harry Brook scored centuries for England to post a mammoth total of 506 runs on board.

snippet.title: Hit 2 Non Spoiler Review | Adivi Sesh, Meenakshi | Sailesh Kolanu, Nani | Telugu Movies | Thyview
snippet.description:
Hello All Welcome to thyview. here is our non-spoiler review of the film Hit 2 directed by DR sailesh Kolanu.

First things first cinema choosaka naa experience cheppali ante, its engaging.decent. baane vundi.2 hours run time helped..but but but meeru usually ilanti thrillers choodaka pothe kanuka meeku khacchitham ga nacchuthundi. ala kakunda meeru naa laaga eppativo criminal minds,Mentalist, ncis, csi, castle nundi monna vacchina mind hunter, mare of eastown, Dahmer documentary daaka ilanti content consume chesunte kanuka meeda ok baane vundi and pedda thrilling ga anipinchaka poina movie end ayinappudu oka satisfaction tho theatre nundi bayataki vastharu.and meelo kontha mandhiki vunde regular questions, Hit 1 kanna bavunda ? i would say yes, this is better written ela anedi detailed ga tharuvatha cheptha.  and next question vacchesi hit2 choodali ante mundu hit1 choodala ? well choosthe konni connections artham avuthai, but choodakapoina hit2 works as a stand alone film.

snippet.title: Jetha ने खाए Daya के हाथ के मज़ेदार पकवान | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | FE 1389 | 29 Nov 2022
snippet.description:
Episode 1389: Jetha ने खाए Daya के हाथ के मज़ेदार पकवान 
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
Even after meeting Big B in real life, Gokuldham residents cannot believe that they have witnessed such a historic moment in their lives. Everyone is replaying the moments again and again in their minds and trying to bask in the glory of meeting Amitabh Bachchan in real life. The Gada family is no different with Daya calling her family and telling them all about it. Jetha is enjoying the tasty dishes prepared by Daya.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 1389
Produced By -  Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा  #sonypal 

Subscribe to Sony Pal: http:/a/www.youtube.com/sonypalindia

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfyXOEyr93G1DSZ-26hoFNNWQ9Jnu9kZu

snippet.description:
"Resham Ka Rumal" has always been a song to sway your legs. Bringing a modern and uplifting rendition with lyrics penned by Rajesh Manthan and a modern mood by Gourov Dasgupta. Sung by Shruti Rane and featuring none other than Divya Agarwal. The video is directed and choreographed by Prince Gupta.

Credits:

Director & Choreographer – Prince Gupta
Singer- Shruti Rane
D.O.P. – Ajay Pandey
Stylist- Jimmy Z
Music – Gourov Dasgupta  
Programmed, mixed and mastered – Som Riggs
Lyricist- Rajesh Manthan                                                                  
Editor -Oswin Reveredo (Shake & Cut Studio)
Asst. editor - Ulleses Correia 
Production house – Prince Gupta Films
Executive Producer - Prayas Choudhary
Assistant Choreographers - Ali Choudary, Rupali Kantharia, Bhavika Sachdeva, Shubham 
Director’s associate- Paraag Choudhary
Art - Amrita Maruti Pawadmal
Divya’s Team:

Make Up- Disha Girish Sanghvi
Assistant - Nirmal Shah and Akshay
Hairstyle- Mohammed Irfan Shaikh
Prince Gupta Film Team: Kamal Singh Bathi , Durgesh Sambariya, Vishal Vedre, Saiprasad Amare , Sujit 

Original Credits:
Original Music Director: Ila Arun, Lalit Sen
Original Singer: Ila Arun
Original Lyrics: Ila Arun

Lyrics:
Dum dum damke jhumka mera, maarda lashkaara,

Rang birangi odhni main, odh aayi yaara,

Sun zara bole kya dil ka iktara..

Resham ka.. haan
Resham ka roomal gale mein daal ke,  tu aaja na.. aa wait karoon main, 

Main cherry wali lipistick lagake, arey.. kab se khadi hoon darwajje pe..

Resham ka.... haan

Meri nathani haale dole, mera bichhua chham bole, Re ,

Meri nathani haale dole, mera bichhua chham chham bole..

Meri laal chunariya, sar se sarakati jaaye

Dildaar mere main, haan branded wala perfume lagaake are, kab se chhupi hoon mai rajaayi mein, o o

Resham ka.. Haan

Jab jab dekhoon chehra tera,
Hosh huye aawaara
Bajaran teri huyi main,
Tu mera banjaara,

Dholna  sabse tu mujhko hai pyaara,

Resham ka...
Resham ka roomal gale mein daalke tu aa jaana, darling mere main,. Main mehngi waali goggle lagake yaham  kab se khadi hoon darwajje pe..oo

Resham ka...

Mai cherry wali lipistick lagake are
Mai mehengi wali goggle lagake aha
Han branded wala perfume lagake  

Kabse khadi hun darawajje pe,o o o
Resham Ka.. Haa

snippet.description:

It's not limited to your romantic partners but for anyone who you would go to the moon and back. The lyrics written by Kunaal will take you on the ride of exploring the enchanting journey of failing to know how and why you love someone backed with Amaal's fervent composition that gives my vocals a perfect canvas to articulate my emotions. I sincerely hope that my fans experience 'Sun Maahi' and get transported into their own world of unexplained, beautiful, and surreal love-stories.

snippet.title: WOH – Ikka x Dino James x Badshah (Official Lyric Video) | Def Jam India
snippet.description:
India’s Hip-Hop superstars Ikka, Dino James & Badshah come together to channel their inner hopeless romanticism on ‘Woh.’ The track captures the immense hurt, emotions and male vulnerability which comes at the backdrop of a heartbreak. ‘Woh’ is one of the very few records which portray a man’s emotions with evocative honesty and reveals the softer side of him. Dino James pens down the difficulties behind missing someone that he has loved. He feels helpless and apologetic. Ikka feels his heart sinking as he is incapable of fixing the broken relationship and cannot deal with the heartache anymore. Badshah’s verse starts by asserting that it is okay for a man to break down and go through the gut-wrenching feeling of a fleeting romance. ‘Woh’ is an extremely personal track which is bound to shake you if you have ever loved someone.

Hailing from a lower-middle-class family, Kiran is a selfish and arrogant girl who aspires to achieve a lifestyle through mending her ways and taking shortcuts. Kiran’s mother Nusrat Ara is aware of her daughter’s nature and doesn’t stop her from doing anything. On the contrary, Ujala is a well-mannered and beautiful girl who lives with Kiran’s family and strives to become independent. 

Zarbab, a handsome young man who belongs to an influential and wealthy family. His first meeting with Kiran turns out to be magical as he falls in love at first sight. Kiran sees him as a way to advance forward in life and builds a web of lies and deceit around Zarbab. On the other hand, Ujala is forced to live a life deprived of love and unfulfilled dreams.

Will Ujala ever find the love and respect that she deserves? After building her life on lies and deception, how long will Kiran be able to conceal the truth?

snippet.title: Forgotten Malayalam Movies S04 E07 | The Soorya Trilogy | Malayalam Movie Review Funny | Indrajith
snippet.description:
ആയിരക്കണക്കിന് പുസ്തകങ്ങൾ ഇനി ദിവസവും 1 രൂപയിൽ താഴെ ചിലവിൽ വർഷം മുഴുവനും കേട്ട് അറിയൂ.
Download India's no 1 audio book platform: https://kukufm.page.link/DJ4EnXTWvJc9CoGt9

50% ഓഫർ ലഭിക്കുവാൻ ഈ കൂപ്പൺ ഉപയോഗിക്കൂ : ANB200

Forgotten Malayalam Movies is a movie review series where we review some of the greatest (read : worst) movies in malayalam.

Which is your favourite trilogy? The Dark Knight Trilogy? Lord of the Rings Trilogy? Harihar Nagar Trilogy? Nadodikkaattu trilogy? snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3630 - 1 Dec 2022 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3630: 
--------------------------------------------------------
Jethalal reaches his shop and finds out that it's still closed. Even after waiting around for a bit, there is no sign of Nattu Kaka or Bagha. He even loses a customer as they see that the shop is closed. When they finally arrive, Nattu Kaka and Bagha start fighting. Jetha rushes them to open the shop first and then decides to solve the matter. When the real reason for the feud is revealed Jethalal becomes a mediator and makes them understand the point of view of another. Will Bagha and Nattu Kaka reconcile now?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3630, 1 Dec 2022
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :

snippet.title: Match Highlights - Poland 0:2 Argentina - FIFA World Cup Qatar 2022 | JioCinema & Sports18
snippet.description:
A game that had major ramifications for all teams in Group C. Argentina & Poland clashed at Stadium 974, knowing a draw would take both sides through provided the other result too ends in their favour.

But nothing could be risked and that's how both sides played. Lionel Messi had a penalty saved in the first half & a tense half appeared to be on the cards. But Alexis Mac Allister with a scuffed effort put Argentina ahead & Julian Alvarez doubled the lead for the South Americans. Lionel Scaloni's side attacked at the closing minutes only for their attempt to be cleared off the line.

Despite the outcome of this high-octane clash, both Poland and Argentina marched into the #Qatar2022 Round of 16 as Mexico fell short against Saudi Arabia.

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Siyani Episode 107 - [Eng Sub] - Anmol Baloch - Mohsin Abbas Haider - Saniya Shamshad - 30th November 2022

Hailing from a lower-middle-class family, Kiran is a selfish and arrogant girl who aspires to achieve a lifestyle through mending her ways and taking shortcuts. Kiran’s mother Nusrat Ara is aware of her daughter’s nature and doesn’t stop her from doing anything. On the contrary, Ujala is a well-mannered and beautiful girl who lives with Kiran’s family and strives to become independent. 

Zarbab, a handsome young man who belongs to an influential and wealthy family. His first meeting with Kiran turns out to be magical as he falls in love at first sight. Kiran sees him as a way to advance forward in life and builds a web of lies and deceit around Zarbab. On the other hand, Ujala is forced to live a life deprived of love and unfulfilled dreams.

Will Ujala ever find the love and respect that she deserves? After building her life on lies and deception, how long will Kiran be able to conceal the truth?

Written By: Sadia Akhtar
Directed By: Ali Akbar
Produced By: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Anmol Baloch - Kiran

Mohsin Abbas Haider - Zarbaab

snippet.title: Match Highlights - Costa Rica 2:4 Germany - FIFA World Cup Qatar 2022 | JioCinema & Sports18
snippet.description:
For the 2nd #FIFAWorldCup edition running, Germany have been knocked out in the group stage. The four-time world champions needed to win & also needed Spain to do them a favour by beating Japan.

Serge Gnabry put the Germans ahead in the 10th minute but Yeltsin Tejeda & Juan Pablo Vargas turned it around in the second half to revive Costa Rican hopes of a surprise qualification.

Germany were now left needing a massive result owing to Japan's turnaround in the other game. They went on to reclaim the lead through Kai Havertz's brace. Niclas Fullkrug got in on the act to make it 4-2 but that left Hansi Flick's side short by five goals, sending both sides out of the competition.

snippet.title: Episode 517 - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Full Episode | तारक मेहता का उल्टा चश्मा
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.
